# Cloudflare Pages 响应头配置
# 对 HTML 页面禁用缓存（no-store），避免运营商/代理等中间缓存缓存旧页面导致看到旧版。
# 静态资源（assets 下的 css/js/img）不在此列，仍按文件名 + ?v= 版本号正常缓存。

/
  Cache-Control: no-store
/index.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
/committee
  Cache-Control: no-store
/committee.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
/committee-history
  Cache-Control: no-store
/committee-history.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
/project
  Cache-Control: no-store
/project.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
/activity
  Cache-Control: no-store
/activity.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
/activity_category
  Cache-Control: no-store
/activity_category.html
  Cache-Control: no-store
